          ρ (rho)
         </div>
         <div class="text-slate-400 mt-1">
          Densidad del aire
         </div>
         <div class="mono text-slate-200 mt-1">
          1.225 kg/m³
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-700/30">
         <div class="mono text-cyan-400 font-bold">
          A
         </div>
         <div class="text-slate-400 mt-1">
          Área barrida
         </div>
         <div class="mono text-slate-200 mt-1"><span id="areaDisplay">4.00</span> m²
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-700/30">
         <div class="mono text-cyan-400 font-bold">
          v
         </div>
         <div class="text-slate-400 mt-1">
          Velocidad viento
         </div>
         <div class="mono text-slate-200 mt-1"><span id="vDisplay">5.0</span> m/s
         </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/40 rounded-lg p-3 border border-slate-700/30">
         <div class="mono text-cyan-400 font-bold">
          Cp
         </div>
         <div class="text-slate-400 mt-1">
          Coef. potencia
         </div>
         <div class="mono text-slate-200 mt-1">
          0.35 (Darrieus)
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div><!-- Turbine dimensions -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur rounded-3xl border border-slate-700/50 p-6 card-glow">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <i data-lucide="ruler" class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400"></i>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Dimensiones del molino</h2>
       </div>
       <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div>
         <label for="diameterInput" class="text-xs text-slate-400 mono uppercase tracking-wider">Diámetro (m)</label> <input type="number" id="diameterInput" value="2" min="0.5" max="10" step="0.1" class="mt-1 w-full bg-slate-950/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 mono text-cyan-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-cyan-500 transition">
        </div>
        <div>
         <label for="heightInput" class="text-xs text-slate-400 mono uppercase tracking-wider">Altura (m)</label> <input type="number" id="heightInput" value="2" min="0.5" max="10" step="0.1" class="mt-1 w-full bg-slate-950/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg px-3 py-2 mono text-cyan-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-cyan-500 transition">
        </div>
       </div>
       <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-3 mono">* Área barrida = Diámetro × Altura (rotor vertical)</p>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div><!-- Bottom: Step-by-step + Challenge -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6">
     <!-- Step by step calculation -->
     <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur rounded-3xl border border-slate-700/50 p-6 card-glow">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
       <i data-lucide="list-ordered" class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-400"></i>
       <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold">Cálculo paso a paso</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3 mono text-sm">
       <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-950/40 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
        <span class="step-number font-bold text-lg">1</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
         <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
          Calcular área barrida
         </div>
         <div class="text-cyan-200">
          A = D × H = <span id="s1">2 × 2 = 4.00</span> m²
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-950/40 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
        <span class="step-number font-bold text-lg">2</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
         <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
          Elevar velocidad al cubo
         </div>
         <div class="text-cyan-200">
          v³ = <span id="s2">5.0³ = 125.00</span> m³/s³
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-slate-950/40 rounded-lg border border-slate-800">
        <span class="step-number font-bold text-lg">3</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
         <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
          Aplicar fórmula completa
         </div>
         <div class="text-cyan-200 text-xs">
          P = 0.5 × 1.225 × <span id="s3a">4.00</span> × <span id="s3b">125.00</span> × 0.35
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/40 to-emerald-950/40 rounded-lg border border-green-500/30">
        <span class="step-number font-bold text-lg">=</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
         <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
          Potencia generada
         </div>
         <div class="text-green-300 text-xl font-bold">
          <span id="finalPower">107.19</span> W <span class="text-xs text-slate-400 font-normal ml-2">(<span id="finalPowerKw">0.107</span> kW)</span>
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div><!-- Challenge -->
     <div class="bg-slate-900/60 backdrop-blur rounded-3xl border border-slate-700/50 p-6 card-glow">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
        <i data-lucide="target" class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400"></i>
        <h2 id="challenge_title" class="text-lg font-semibold">Desafío del día</h2>
       </div><button id="newChallengeBtn" class="mono text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 hover:bg-slate-700 border border-slate-700 transition flex items-center gap-1"> <i data-lucide="refresh-cw" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Nuevo </button>
      </div>
      <div id="challengeBox" class="bg-slate-950/40 rounded-xl p-4 border border-slate-800 mb-4">
       <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 leading-relaxed" id="challengeText">Un molino Darrieus tiene 3m de diámetro y 4m de altura. Hoy el viento sopla a <span class="text-yellow-300 font-bold">8 m/s</span>. ¿Cuánta potencia genera?</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
       <label for="answerInput" class="text-xs text-slate-400 mono uppercase tracking-wider">Tu respuesta (Watts)</label>
       <div class="flex gap-2">
        <input type="number" id="answerInput" placeholder="Escribe tu cálculo..." class="flex-1 bg-slate-950/60 border border-slate-700 rounded-lg px-4 py-3 mono text-cyan-200 focus:outline-none focus:border-yellow-500 transition placeholder-slate-600"> <button id="checkBtn" class="px-5 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-green-500 hover:from-cyan-400 hover:to-green-400 rounded-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 transition flex items-center gap-2"> <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-4 h-4"></i> Verificar </button>
       </div>
